{"tid":1867701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國行為藝術家玩轉Google Maps　單人匹馬炮製「虛擬塞車」","createTime":"2020-02-07T09:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T11:45:25.000Z","uid":253829,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0966156278d2614bfcb789592cf32e58cb686099","tid":1867701,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:40:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k5eL_al_m7Q&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dk5eL_al_m7Q%26feature%3Demb_title&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=8f2afff8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k5eL_al_m7Q&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scdn.slashgear.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/google-maps-hacks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscdn.slashgear.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2Fgoogle-maps-hacks.jpg&h=cd9d5d06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三年前來自德國柏林的行為藝術家 Simon Weckert 發現了 Google Map 的「漏洞」，即是 Google Map 僅是透過智能手機用戶的數量來判斷該路段的路況是否壅塞。為了讓人們注意到我們視為理所當然的方便服務並對之感恩，Simon Weckert 早先從朋友和購物商城中租借了共計 99 支智慧型手機，將它們全數放在一個紅色塑膠拖車並開啟 Google Map，隨著他緩慢地行走在街道上，Simon Weckert 成功地讓 Google Map 將該路段誤判為道路壅塞，然而事實上沒有人和一輛車子經過。<br />\n<br />\n對於 Simon Weckert 這次的行為藝術，Google 表示：「Google Map 的路況資訊持續地透過各式各樣的來源更新，包括匿名的用戶資訊等等，我們認為這次的行為藝術相當有創意，也很感謝它讓我們能夠試著讓我們的軟體更完善。」隨後 Google 也補充表示，目前 Google Map 僅能夠區別車輛與機車，但還沒有辦法分別出與今回類似的狀況。"},{"pid":"10754332741cf96d5c8d10c614e724cad5b20437","tid":1867701,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:57:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9847e64e3d1378e4f8731e18584a9c911d00855d","tid":1867701,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df12237fba5ee7ac330ad829c31cc2995ab3622f","tid":1867701,"uid":103861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:45:25.000Z","msg":"欣賞google嘅回應方式"}]}